{"tid":2487271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人知道，當年梁天琦要坐咁耐　係因為有人篤灰？","createTime":"2021-04-13T12:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T12:31:25.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d84d8d3f6b7d1975bd0198bde657b56ae384bfa4","tid":2487271,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rootinhksoul2020/posts/1392119074477399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frootinhksoul2020%2Fposts%2F1392119074477399&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11LvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=b80fe09b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rootinhksoul2020/posts/1392119074477399</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：本小姐<br />\n<br />\n有幾多人知道，當年梁天琦要坐咁耐<br />\n係因為有人篤灰？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLangley Chan:<br />\n唔係督灰<br />\n跟我講一次<br />\n係老屈<br />\n口供屈係梁天琦於魚蛋革命策動並指揮群眾<br />\n<br />\nMatias Sweetpotato:<br />\n佢對天琦無篤灰，篤灰係有做過先有得篤，佢呢個係老屈<br />\n不過佢仲好似有篤其他人灰"},{"pid":"3969b602118ef3b453e4234b494da14115f0fb5d","tid":2487271,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05c796808ac2c04e1c5dc4ba1b697780ae3e74d","tid":2487271,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係呢個page"},{"pid":"b821c2905bea4ced9b59b811b8221d5b31d4eb6d","tid":2487271,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"梁天琦係湖北武漢人"}]}